{"lemma":"خُلْدُ","slug":"خُلْدُ","root":"خ.ل.د","root_slug":"خ-ل-د","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ل-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خُلْد","root":"خلد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":6},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":14},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11234","n11235","n11237","n11238","n11239","n11240"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to last forever, to be everlasting"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be immortal"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to abide forever"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to remain, to stay"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rest"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make eternal, to make everlasting","examples":[{"text":"يَطُوفُ عَلَيْهِمْ وِلْدَانٌ مُّخَلَّدُونَ","english":"There will circulate among them young boys made eternal."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to perpetuate, to make immortal"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make ineffaceable, to make unforgettable"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to remain, to stay, to abide, to linger"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to grow very old, to enjoy a long life, to be long-lived"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"infinite duration, endless time, perpetuity, eternity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mind, heart, spirit, temper","examples":[{"text":"مَا دَارَ فِي خَلَدِ الْأَيَّامِ لِي فَرَحٌ / أَبَا عُبَادَةَ حَتَّى دُرْتَ فِي خَلَدِي"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mole-rat"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mole","tags":["Arabic","Modern","Standard","proscribed"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew חלד (khéled, “world, era”) and Ge'ez ኀለደ (ḫälädä, “to last long”).\n\nFrom Aramaic חוּלְדּא / ܚܘܠܕܐ (ḥuldā, “mole”). Compare Hebrew חולד (khóled)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11234","headword_ar":"خَلَدَ","root":"xld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwdN","text_ar":"خُلُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulodN","text_ar":"خُلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * A, L, K, * [but the latter is not said to be an inf. n. in the first nor in the last of these lexicons, and is perhaps a simple subst.,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He remained, stayed, dwelt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqaAma","text_ar":"اَقَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he remained, stayed, dwelt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"page_break","n":784},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode, long;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTaAla AlA_iqaAmapa","text_ar":"اَطَالَ الاـِقَامَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bimakaAnK","text_ar":"بِمَكَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY makaAnK","text_ar":"اـِلَى مَكَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a place"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axld","text_ar":"اخلد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xl~d","text_ar":"خلّد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he remained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"continued, incessantly, always, endlessly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for ever;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, K; *) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baqiYa","text_ar":"بَقِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, L, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAma","text_ar":"دَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAma baqaAw^uhu","text_ar":"دَامَ بَقَاوُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, L;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY daArK","text_ar":"فِى دَارٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an abode, not going forth from it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he remained, stayed, dwelt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode, for ever,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perpetually,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in Paradise, (A, L,) or in Hell. (A.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalada","text_ar":"خَلَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ham p. 70, and L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalodN","text_ar":"خَلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaladN","text_ar":"خَلَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (thus in the L,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwdN","text_ar":"خُلُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axld","text_ar":"اخلد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Ham ubi suprà;) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was slow in becoming hoary,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when advanced in years;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as though he were created to continue for ever. (L.) ―         -b3-  See also 4, in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","A","L","Msb","K","Ham"]},{"entry_id":"n11235","headword_ar":"خلّد","root":"xld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", as a trans. v.: see 4.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He adorned"},{"kind":"text","text":"a girl ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with bracelets,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other ornaments"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see the pass. part. n.), or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with earrings."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA.)       -A3-  As an intrans. v.: see 1: ―         -b2-  and see also 4."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n11237","headword_ar":"خَلْدٌ","root":"xld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n11238","headword_ar":"خُلْدٌ","root":"xld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalada","text_ar":"خَلَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, L,) [or a simple subst.] syn. with [the inf. n.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwdN","text_ar":"خُلُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxulodu","text_ar":"الخُلْدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAru Alxulodi","text_ar":"دَارُ الخُلْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) [the latter signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The abode of the state of perpetual existence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Paradise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Paradises:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the world to come."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bracelet:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an earring;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaladapN","text_ar":"خَلَدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiladapN","text_ar":"خِلَدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) which last signifies [also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ornaments for the person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"collectively; (TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulodapN","text_ar":"خُلْدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[if this be not a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiladapN","text_ar":"خِلَدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.)       -A3-  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mole;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blind rat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalodN","text_ar":"خَلْدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"julo*N","text_ar":"جُلْذٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jl*","text_ar":"جلذ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a species of rat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilodN","text_ar":"خِلْدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) or one of the names of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^or","text_ar":"فَاْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (IAar:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a species of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of rats called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiro*aAn","text_ar":"جِرْذَان"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blind"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, L, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by nature,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, L, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having no eyes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inhabiting the deserts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) Lth says that the sing. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilodN","text_ar":"خِلْدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilodaAnN","text_ar":"خِلْدَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": in the T it is said that the sing. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilodapN","text_ar":"خِلْدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilodaAnN","text_ar":"خِلْدَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which is very strange: (L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a blind beast"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that lives"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneath the ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having no eyes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that likes the smell of onions and leeks; so that if either of these be put over its hole, it comes forth and is caught: if its upper lip be hung upon a person affected with a quartan fever, it cures him; and its brain, mixed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moistened, with oil of roses, and used as an ointment, dispels the maladies termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaraS","text_ar":"البَرَص"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albahaq","text_ar":"البَهَق"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqawaAbiY","text_ar":"القَوَابِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljarab","text_ar":"الجَرَب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkalaf","text_ar":"الكَلَف"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxanaAziyr","text_ar":"الخَنَازِير"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and every eruption upon the body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaAji*u","text_ar":"مَنَاجِذُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) or, as in some copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaAjidu","text_ar":"مَنَاجِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the unpointed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"d","text_ar":"د"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) is used as its pl, like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaADN","text_ar":"مَخَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalifapN","text_ar":"خَلِفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L, K.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A species of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qub~arap","text_ar":"قُبَّرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lark"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.)"}],"source_refs":["A","L","T","K","IAar","Lth","S","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n11239","headword_ar":"خِلْدٌ","root":"xld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulodN","text_ar":"خُلْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n11240","headword_ar":"خَلَدٌ","root":"xld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heart:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axolaAdN","text_ar":"اَخْلَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqaEa *`lika fiY xaladiY","text_ar":"وَقَعَ ذٰلِكَ فِى خَلَدِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That came into my mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heart."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K"]}]}}